Cocaygne. Interpretation: 1) Gula and Desidia or/and; 2) They don't try to get the good they want: 2 sleep - clerk is waiting for the good to come, knight looks longingly to the good - but if they don't do anything themselves they won't get anything in the land of Cocaygne: with other words : praise of work.
